ease-party-30-years-on-3495553">《Smashing Pumpkins》重现 Tower Records 30 年前经典的“Siamese Dream”发行派对</a>后，首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
据报道，瑞典帮派成员利用 Spotify 洗钱https://www.nme.com/news/music/swedish-gang-members-reportedly-using-spotify-to-launder-money-3495551?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=swedish-gang-members-reportedly-using- Spotify 洗钱Emma WilkesSat, 09 Sep 2023 16:40:21 +0000 Music NewsNewsSpotify https://www.nme.com/?p=3495551 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/spotify-logo-phone-screen.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Spotify" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/spotify-logo-phone-screen.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/spotify-logo-phone-screen-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/spotify-logo-phone-screen-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/spotify-logo-phone-screen-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/spotify-logo-phone-screen-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/spotify-logo-phone-screen-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>帮派成员将脏钱兑换成比特币，然后用比特币为有帮派协会的艺术家获取假流</p><p>据报道<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/swedish-gang-members-reportedly-using-spotify-to-launder-money-3495551">，瑞典帮派成员利用 Spotify 洗钱的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/spotify-logo-phone-screen.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Spotify" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/spotify-logo-phone-screen.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/spotify-logo-phone-screen-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/spotify-logo-phone-screen-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/spotify-logo-phone-screen-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/spotify-logo-phone-screen-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/spotify-logo-phone-screen-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据<a href="https://www.musicbusinessworldwide.com/multiple-criminal-gang-members-confirm-theyve-used-spotify-for-money-laundering-in-bombshell-new-report-in-sweden/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">瑞典一家报纸</a>报道，瑞典的帮派成员据称一直在使用<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/spotify">Spotify</a>洗钱。</p><p>该出版物<em>《Svenska Dagbladet》</em>报道称，帮派成员将从毒品交易、抢劫、欺诈和暗杀任务中获得的资金转换成比特币，然后用比特币为与帮派有联系的艺术家获取假流。然后，他们稍后收取支付给这些流的钱。</p><p> <em>Svenska Dagbladet</em>采访的一位消息人士表示，Spotify“非常适合招募人员”，因为帮派成员可以利用流行艺术家，特别是瑞典黑帮说唱界的流行艺术家，作为他们活动的幌子。 “如果你是一个网络公司，你想吸引孩子们，并且你有一位正在走红的说唱歌手，那么这对你来说就完成了一半，”消息人士说。</p><p><a href="https://cnm.fr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">法国的一项研究</a>发现，Spotify 等服务上的流媒体中有 3% 存在欺诈行为。 2021 年检测到的绝大多数（84.5%）来自嘻哈艺术家。然而，嘻哈音乐是法国流媒体市场上最受欢迎的流派，2021 年该国录制的嘻哈流媒体总数中只有 0.4% 被确定为欺诈。 </p><figure id="attachment_3182187" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3182187" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3182187" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ManwithSpotifyonphone.jpg" alt="Spotify" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ManwithSpotifyonphone.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ManwithSpotifyonphone-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ManwithSpotifyonphone-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ManwithSpotifyonphone-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ManwithSpotifyonphone-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ManwithSpotifyonphone-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3182187" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：Alamy Stock Photo。</figcaption></figure><p> Spotify 拒绝对<em>Svenska Dagbladet</em>的报道发表评论，并坚称他们“没有证据”表明该流媒体平台存在洗钱行为。</p><p>在 Spotify 的其他新闻中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift)</a>创造了历史，成为<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/spotify">Spotify</a>上第<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-becomes-first-female-artist-with-100million-monthly-spotify-listeners-3490768">一位每月听众突破 1 亿的女艺术家</a>。</p><p>今年早些时候，该流媒体<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/spotify-increases-subscription-prices-in-uk-and-us-first-time-3472555">首次提高了订阅价格</a>，影响了英国和美国的用户。</p><p>在英国，Premium 计划现在的费用为每月 10.99 英镑，高于之前的每月 9.99 英镑。针对多个用户的各种计划也每月上涨 1 英镑，其中 Duo 订阅现价为 14.99 英镑，家庭计划（涵盖 6 人）现价为 17.99 英镑。到目前为止，唯一保持不变的计划是 Spotify 学生订阅，仍为每月 5.99 英镑。</p><p></p><p>据报道<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/swedish-gang-members-reportedly-using-spotify-to-launder-money-3495551">，瑞典帮派成员利用 Spotify 洗钱的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
